These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, amber, ivory, yellow
House: ranch-style, art-deco, gothic-revival, townhouse
1. the art-deco house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
2. the person who likes grey is the townhouse house##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
4. the person who likes amber is on the left of the townhouse house##1
5. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Color          | yellow | ivory | amber | grey   |
| House   | art-deco  | ranch-style     | gothic-revival   | townhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, havana, game, fonseca
There 4 different types of food: plum, watermelon, blueberry, pepper
1. the fonseca-smoker is the person eating watermelon##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | game | fonseca | havana | chaman    |
| Food   | blueberry    | watermelon      | plum | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, taxi, van
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, hedgehog, fish
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the person driving the bike is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Transport         | bike | van | taxi   | subway |
| Pet   | ferret   | hedgehog | fish | goat         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, nurse, pilot
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, poppy, rose, iris
1. the person who growspoppy is the pilot##1
2. the lawyer is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
3. the lawyer is on the left of the analyst##1
4. the lawyer is on the right of the pilot##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | pilot | lawyer | analyst  | nurse      |
| Flower         | poppy | iris   | rose | aconite |

