.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, analyst, journalist, nurse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, june, december, november
1. the analyst is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the journalist##1
3. the nurse is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Job   | nurse | journalist | analyst | security-guard |
| Birthday    | july       | november | december | june     |

