.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, car, trike
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, gardening, camping, video-games
1. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | trike | car | snowmobile | tram |
| Hobby           | baking      | camping | video-games | gardening    |

