.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, colombian, german, indonesian
City: nizza, berlin, boston, hamburg
1. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
2. the indonesian is on the far right##1
3. the german is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
5. the colombian is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Nationality   | german | colombian | pakistani | indonesian  |
| City           | boston | nizza | hamburg       | berlin |

