2. the person traveling to berlin is the person who likes ivory##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes white##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Color         | chestnut | white      | ebony | ivory |
| City   | hamburg          | boston | edinburgh     | berlin    |

