3. the person who growsazalea is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
