.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, frog, ferret, hedgehog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, swimming, tennis, sailing
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Pet    | turtle | ferret  | frog | hedgehog |
| Sport   | sailing | tennis | swimming          | soccer    |

