.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking, photography, video-games
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, december, april
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Hobby      | photography | filmmaking  | gardening | video-games |
| Birthday   | june  | december | april           | october   |

