3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| City   | venice | hannover | miami | prague  |
| Sport           | surfing | badminton      | golf | snowboarding |

