.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, august, september
There 4 different types of food: avocado, grapes, grapefruit, strawberry
1. the person eating strawberry is the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | august | october  | june | september   |
| Food        | grapefruit | grapes | strawberry    | avocado |

