.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, january, april, february
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, lacrosse, baseball
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday      | june   | february | january   | april      |
| Sport   | climbing | baseball      | cricket | lacrosse |

