.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
4 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, billiard, snooker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, hot-chocolate, juice
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing billiard##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Game         | mah-jongg | billiard | snooker | chess |
| Beverage   | juice     | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk      | lemonade   |

