.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, surfing, swimming, water-polo
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, freelancer, dressmaker, engineer
1. the dancer is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is the engineer##1
5. the dancer is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport   | skiing | swimming | surfing | water-polo   |
| Job     | dressmaker  | dancer    | freelancer       | engineer |

 